	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="">fun</a> <a id="fs8" href="#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Sat, Feb 28th 12:44 AM 2004</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=13763"><span id=" ">Yuktii</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">185 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Good [4.26]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Horror is 430 / tick. 430 + 40% is 602. However, this percentage is a lie, in actuallity, it's between zero and x percent for each tick. So you use half of the value as the average (i.e., Burning Affliction is an average of 10% extra damage and this is an average of 20% extra damage). <br/><br/>So, this makes Horror do an average of 516 per tick, Embracing Darkness 82, Saryrn's Kiss 229, Splurt will do about 2300 total, etc. Pretty nice :)<br/><br/>But any necro has to like 220 HPs and 20 STA (which will add another 100 HPs with no ND AA), fun fun :)</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Yuktii - 70 Necromancer 461AAs<br/>Foogie - 70 Ranger 325AAs<br/>Gazuk - 67 SK 81AAs<br/>Daaniel - 66 Rogue 121AAs<br/>Floppee - 61 Cleric<br/>alt overflow error in sig.c (284)<br/>Quellious Server</td></tr>
